HEADWORD: Forsay
<hw>For*say"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>forsecgan</ets> to accuse; pref. <ets>for-</ets> +
<ets>secgan</ets> to say.]</ety> <def>To forbid; to renounce; to
forsake; to deny.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
